{
  "texts": [
    "Data preprocessing in the study mainly includes the following aspects:",
    "In the process of data acquisition, many reasons may cause the incompleteness of collected data.",
    "For datasets that lack a column name, define the column name to clarify the meaning of the attribute.",
    "Since medical data involves different individuals, and individual differences exist among patients, it is easy to introduce greater errors if the missing values are filled by mean, median, chain equation and other methods hastily.",
    "Therefore, data samples containing missing values are removed in this paper to ensure the integrity of each analysis sample."
  ]
}